p-content/uploads/2025/02/come-together@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/come-together@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/come-together@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/come-together@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/come-together@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>聚集在一起的节日为2025年的阵容增加了更多名称，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-snuts">Snuts</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nieve-ella">Nieve Ella</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cribs">Cribs</a> 。在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-snuts-millennials-review-lyrics-tracklist-3590819">snuts  - “千禧一代”评论：高能吉他国歌</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的分期付款定于6月4日至8日之间，并将在纽卡斯尔的镇沼地举行。</p><p>加入该法案的第一波浪潮是在2024年底分享的，当时宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-newcastles-inaugural-come-together-festival-2025-with-kaiser-chiefs-perrie-and-more-3812625">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">莱昂（Leon）的国王</a>都被锁定为头条新闻。</p><p>现在，组织者分享了第二波艺术家，与莱昂国王队在6月8日星期日的阵容中宣布了另外19场将登上舞台的行为。其中包括苏格兰独立集团The Snuts，他们在2023年将他们的最后一张专辑 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-snuts-millennials-review-lyrics-tracklist-3590819">“ Millenials”</a>放弃了，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-snuts-millennials-review-lyrics-tracklist-3590819"><em>NME</em>描述</a>为在他们的节目中成为“全征用活力的活力”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-reytons">雷顿（Reytons）</a>也加入了阵容 - 去年在罗瑟勒姆（Rotherham） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-reytons-announce-20000-capacity-outdoor-show-rotherham-buy-tickets-3507594">播放了20,000个能力的家庭演出</a>后，将登上舞台，以庆祝最近的LP <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-reytons-announce-third-album-ballad-of-a-bystander-pre-order-new-single-let-me-breathe-listen-3505969">“旁观者的民谣”</a> ，也将表演添加到他们的演出中。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-reveal-support-acts-for-all-points-east-2025-reunion-3807780">与MacCabees</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-announce-homecoming-employment-20th-anniversary-show-with-razorlight-the-cribs-and-more-3799217">Kaiser Chiefs</a>一起演出的行程。 </p><figure id="attachment_3089903" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3089903" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3089903" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty.jpg" alt="鼻子" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/the-snuts-live-2021-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3089903" class="wp-caption-text"> SNUTS的杰克·科克伦（Jack Cochrane）在阅读节上演出。图片来源：Simone Joyner/Getty Images。</figcaption></figure><p>其他新名称包括独立流行歌手和<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/nieve-ella-26-08-2024-3787148">前<em>NME</em>封面明星</a>Nieve Ella，她因她的“ Watch It Ache and Ache and Bleeed&#39;Ep&#39;的EP和Art-Pop艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/du-blonde">Du Blonde</a>和Newcastle的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chloe-slater">Chloe</a>获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nieve-ella-watch-it-ache-and-bleed-review-radar-3803568">五星级评论。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chloe-slater">Slater</a> 。</p><p>汤姆·A <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luvcat">·</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girlband">史密斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/overpass">（</a> Tom A.<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucia">露西亚（Lucia）和最好的男孩</a>都完成了剩余的法案，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-fender">利亚姆·芬德（Liam Fender）</a> ，亚伦·罗（Aaron Rowe），皇家农民，巴什特（Basht），德尔德（Dolder）和科特尼·迪克森（Cortney Dixon）也完成了。</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcome-together-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F5515079" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处的门票</a>。</p><p> Teg Europe董事总经理Toby Leighton-Pope说：“我们很高兴在Come Festival上宣布如此多样化和才华横溢的阵容。” “很高兴看到来自国家和地方背景的许多新的支持行为，为这个开创性的城市中心节融合在一起。我们认为，建立和新兴艺术家的这种融合将为所有与会者提供难忘的经历。” </p><figure id="attachment_3182068" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3182068" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3182068" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing.jpg" alt="婴儿床" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/the-cribs-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3182068" class="wp-caption-text">婴儿床的瑞安·贾曼（Ryan Jarman）（图片：Lorne Thomson/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>在另一个新公告中，该活动的官方慈善合作伙伴被任命为格雷厄姆·韦利爵士基金会。该慈善机构致力于帮助，激发和教育东北地区的儿童和年轻人。它将满足所有运营成本（包括员工和行政管理），以便所有筹集和捐赠的资金将直接用于良好的事业。<a href="https://sirgrahamwyliefoundation.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>了解有关基础的更多信息。</p><p>至于罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">这位</a>明星将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-newcastles-inaugural-come-together-festival-2025-with-kaiser-chiefs-perrie-and-more-3812625">在第一天（6月4日）成为头条新闻</a>- 标志着他自2015年以来在纽卡斯尔（Newcastle）的第一场演出。</p><p>去年11月分享该消息时，还宣布凯撒酋长，佩里（Perrie），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andrew-cushin">安德鲁·库辛（Andrew Cushin</a> ），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lottery-winners">彩票获奖者</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nell-mescal">内尔·梅斯卡尔（Nell Mescal）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guy-sebastian">盖伊·塞巴斯蒂安（Guy Sebastian）</a> ，德赛，桑尼·坦妮（Sonny Tennet），查理·弗洛伊德（Charlie Floyd）和哈里埃特·罗斯（Harriet Rose）也将获得2025年的账单。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/he-snuts-nieve-ella-the-cribs-and-more-to-join-kings-of-leon-at-newcastles-come-together-festival-2025-3840317">Snuts，Nieve Ella，Cribs等帖子与Leon的国王在纽卡斯尔的Come Festival 2025一起</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现在NME上。</p> ;
